import styleMemoize from "../../../utils/style-memoize";

import compactButtons from "./types/compact-buttons.style";
import basicButton from "./types/basic-button.style";
import basicInvertedButton from "./types/basic-inverted-button.style";
 
const buttonSpin = keyframes`
  from {
    transform: rotate(0deg);
  }
  to {
    transform: rotate(359deg);
  }
`;
 
export default styleMemoize(function() {
 
  const buttonVars = getButtonVars();
 
  const {
    getSize,
    verticalAlign,
    background,
    textColor,
    fontFamily,
    horizontalMargin,

    loaderLineWidth,
    loaderFillColor,

    iconMargin,

    // iconButtonOpacity,

    labeledIconRightShadow,

    // basicColoredBorderSize,
    // basicBackground,
    // basicFontWeight,

    // basicBoxShadow,

    // basicHoverBackground,
    // basicHoverTextColor,

    // basicFocusBackground,

    // basicDownBackground,
    // basicDownTextColor,
    // basicDownBoxShadow,
    // basicActiveBackground,
    // basicActiveBoxShadow,

    // basicInvertedBackground,

    // invertedTextShadow,
    invertedBorderSize,
    // invertedGroupButtonOffset,
    // invertedVerticalGroupButtonOffset,
 
  } = buttonVars;
 
  const {compactButton,compactIconButton,compactLabeledIconButton} = compactButtons(buttonVars);
 
  return css`
    label: button;
    cursor: pointer;
    display: inline-block;
 
    min-height: 1em;
 
    outline: none;
    border: none;
    vertical-align: ${verticalAlign};
    background: ${background};
    color: ${textColor};
 
    font-family: ${fontFamily};
 
    margin: 0em ${horizontalMargin} ${verticalMargin} 0em;
    padding: ${verticalPadding} ${horizontalPadding} ${unitMath(verticalPadding,"+",shadowOffset)};
 
    text-transform: ${textTransform};
    text-shadow: ${textShadow};
    font-weight: ${fontWeight};
    line-height: ${lineHeight};
    font-style: normal;

    text-decoration: none;

    box-shadow: ${boxShadow};

    will-change: ${willChange}; */}

    &:hover {
      background-color: ${hoverBackgroundColor};
      ${'' /* background-image: ${hoverBackgroundImage}; */}
      ${'' /* box-shadow: ${hoverBoxShadow}; */}
      color: ${hoverColor};
    }
 
    &:hover .icon {
      opacity: ${iconHoverOpacity};
    }
 
    /*--------------
          Focus
    ---------------*/
 
    &:focus {
      background-color: ${focusBackgroundColor};
      color: ${focusColor};
      ${'' /* background-image: ${focusBackgroundImage} !important; */}
      box-shadow: ${focusBoxShadow} !important;
    }
 
    &:focus .icon {
      opacity: ${iconFocusOpacity};
    }
 
    /*--------------
          Down
    ---------------*/
 
    &:active,
    &.active:active {
      background-color: ${downBackgroundColor};
      ${'' /* background-image: ${downBackgroundImage}; */}
      color: ${downColor};
      box-shadow: ${downBoxShadow};
    }
 
    /*--------------
         Active
    ---------------*/
 
    &.active {
      background-color: ${activeBackgroundColor};
      ${'' /* background-image: ${activeBackgroundImage}; */}
      box-shadow: ${activeBoxShadow};
      color: ${activeColor};
    }
    &.active:hover {
      background-color: ${activeHoverBackgroundColor};
      ${'' /* background-image: ${activeHoverBackgroundImage}; */}
      color: ${activeHoverColor};
    }
    &.active:active {
      background-color: ${activeBackgroundColor};
      ${'' /* background-image: ${activeBackgroundImage}; */}
    }
 
    /*-------------------
      Disabled
    --------------------*/
 
    &.disabled,
    &:disabled,
    &.disabled:hover,

      cursor: default;
      opacity: ${disabledOpacity} !important;
      background-image: none !important;
      box-shadow: none;
      pointer-events: none !important;
    }
 
    /* Basic Group With Disabled */
    ${'' /* TODO:
    .ui.basic.buttons .ui.disabled.button {

    } */}
 
    /*--------------

    /* Specificity hack */

      color: ${iconColor}; */}

    }
 
    & > .icon > svg {
      display: block;
    }
 
    &:not(.icon) > .icon:not(.button):not(.dropdown) {
      margin: ${iconMargin};
    }
    &:not(.icon) > .right.icon:not(.button):not(.dropdown) {
      margin: ${rightIconMargin};
    }
 
    /*--------------
        Icon Only
    ---------------*/
 
    &.icon {
      ${iconOnlyButton(buttonVars)}
    }
 
    /*--------------
      Labeled Icon
    ---------------*/
    &.labeled {
      ${labeledIconButton(buttonVars)}
    }
    /* Right Labeled */
    &[class*="right labeled"].icon {
      padding-right: ${labeledIconPadding} !important;
      padding-left: ${horizontalPadding} !important;
    }
    &[class*="right labeled"].icon > .icon {
      left: auto;
      right: 0em;
      border-radius: 0px;
      border-top-right-radius: inherit;
      border-bottom-right-radius: inherit;
      box-shadow: ${labeledIconRightShadow};
    }
 
    /* Fluid Labeled */
    &.fluid[class*="left labeled"].icon,
    &.fluid[class*="right labeled"].icon {
      padding-left: ${horizontalPadding} !important;
      padding-right: ${horizontalPadding} !important;
    }
 
    /*-------------------
        Sizes
    --------------------*/
 
 
 
    ${
      ["mini","tiny","small","medium","large","big","huge","massive"].map((size)=>{
        return `
          &.${size} {
            font-size: ${getSize(size)};
          }
        `;
      }).join(" ")
    }
 
    &.compact {
      ${compactButton}
    }
    &.compact.icon {
      ${compactIconButton}
    }
    &.compact.labeled {
      ${compactLabeledIconButton}
    }
 
 
 
 
    /*-------------------
        Basic
    --------------------*/
 
    &.basic {
      ${basicButton(buttonVars)}
    }
 
    &.basic.inverted {
      ${basicInvertedButton(buttonVars)}
    }
 
 
    /*-------------------
       Inverted
    --------------------*/
 
    &.inverted {
      box-shadow: 0px 0px 0px ${invertedBorderSize} ${white} inset !important;
      background: transparent none;
      color: ${white};
      text-shadow: none !important;
    }
 
    /* States */
 
    /* Hover */
    &.inverted:hover {
      background: ${white};
      box-shadow: 0px 0px 0px ${invertedBorderSize} ${white} inset !important;
      color: ${hoverColor};
    }
 
    /* Active / Focus */
    &.inverted:focus,
    &.inverted.active {
      background: ${white};
      box-shadow: 0px 0px 0px ${invertedBorderSize} ${white} inset !important;
      color: ${focusColor};

    /* Active Focus */
    &.inverted.active:focus {
      background: ${midWhite};
      box-shadow: 0px 0px 0px ${invertedBorderSize} ${midWhite} inset !important;
      color: ${focusColor};
    }
 
    /*-------------------
            Fluid
    --------------------*/
 
    &.fluid {
      width: 100%;
    }
    &.fluid {
      display: block;
    }
 
    /*--------------
        Circular
